data.description: Look no further for your perfect home! This cozy 4-bed, 1-1/2 bath home has had many updates to make it safe for you and your loved ones. Upgrades completed in 2021 include: new sewer line; new sump pump; asbestos basement tile removal, abatement, and new flooring; HVAC system and ductwork cleaned and sanitized; remodeled upper floor; and mostly newer carpeting and fresh paint. The home boasts a number of built-in features, has an extra toilet in the basement, and a NEST thermostat. The roof, windows and gutters were replaced in 2009. The backyard is perfect for entertaining and includes fencing, a fire pit, and a patio. Schedule your showing today to see all that this home has to offer. Perhaps it will be your next home!
